午"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"明明大家齊心罷工就一個手足都唔洗犠牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"係 對唔住<br />\n我話就話聽日唔建議罷<br />\n但手足真要罷 一定配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日試左老細水温<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3f518d86b461449f853b06cc1b491492c3db7e","tid":1708151,"uid":139506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"聽日係咪都唔撚返<br />\n今日俾公司俾激嬲<br />\n佢老母扣我錢，因為遲到<br />\n我話你老母咁多人迫車，我11點返到黎仲想點"},{"pid":"771ce116a255a2689c2dd9ce1fa17d74d8d0c9bf","tid":1708151,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:44:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielam&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=a9941ee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam</a><br />\n1112黎明行動2.0"}]}